metadata.name: DALI
metadata.description:
"I believe in general in death, but in the death of Dali absolutely not. I believe in my death becoming very â€“ almost impossible." - Salvador Dali.

This artwork is a tribute to one of the greatest inspirational masters of all time. The portrait sculpture depicted here is purely hand-sculpted in 3d from scratch.

The sculpting process is on my socials, do check it out.

The person getting this will receive a ztl file for 3d printing.
